The '''2009 Sulawesi superbolide''' was an atmospheric [[Meteoroid#Fireball|fireball]] blast over Indonesia on October 8, 2009, at approximately 03:00 UTC, near the coastal city of [[Watampone]] (colloquially named ''Bone'') in [[South Sulawesi]], island of [[Sulawesi]]. The [[meteorite|meteoritic]] impactor broke up at an estimated height of 15–20&nbsp;km. The impact energy of the [[bolide]] was estimated in the 10 to 50 kiloton [[TNT]] equivalent range with the higher end of this range being more likely. The likely size of the impactor was 5–10 m diameter.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news165.html | publisher=[[NASA]] | title=Asteroid Impactor Reported over Indonesia | work= | date=23 October 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091102151757/http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news165.html | archivedate=2009-11-02 | deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/space/6444895/Asteroid-explosion-over-Indonesia-raises-fears-about-Earths-defences.html | work=The Telegraph | title=Asteroid explosion over Indonesia raises fears about Earth's defences | publisher= | date=27 October 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091029051403/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/space/6444895/Asteroid-explosion-over-Indonesia-raises-fears-about-Earths-defences.html | archivedate=2009-10-29 | deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/33540411/ns/technology_and_science-space | work=NBC News | title=Asteroid explosion was a whopper for Earth | publisher= | date=29 October 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825142803/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/33540411/ns/technology_and_science-space | archivedate=2013-08-25 | deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.space.com/7464-huge-explosion-biggest-space-rock-strike-earth-1994.html | work=Space.com | title=Huge Explosion Was Biggest Space Rock to Strike Earth Since 1994 | publisher= | date=29 October 2009 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110130064252/http://www.space.com/7464-huge-explosion-biggest-space-rock-strike-earth-1994.html | archivedate=2011-01-30 | deadurl=no }}</ref>

